Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里附近就有EXA-DB…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能驾驭它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷吉鲁斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德… 原来是真实存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EXA-DB的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有自我防御技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那种无人机动战士的代号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用EXA-DB的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像生物一样不断进化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正所谓怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它拥有的力量 无人可以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人请回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台机动战士太危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是高达雷吉鲁斯 您只身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 它必须由我击败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我命中注定的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能在这里取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就没有继承伊泽尔坎特大人意志的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承伊泽尔坎特大人的…意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着吧 什么是高达真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须做到和伊泽尔坎特大人那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者更高一层的觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则无法发挥这台高达的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这台高达雷吉鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将胜利掌握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监测到机动战士反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是资源开发小行星聚集的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 没有情报显示周围有友军出战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 为防万一确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的第一要务是前往诺德拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行攻略拉·格拉密斯要塞的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没空沿途沾花惹草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续监视 有情况汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代号希德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13年前 让你身负重伤的怪物又露面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不清楚敌人的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这家伙袭击的舰船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是B班 请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来 这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 明明只是调查一艘漂流船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友军机？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰弗里 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德出现 证明EXA-DB就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会在这个节骨眼上遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要亲手摧毁EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必通知歌姬号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不只是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是清剿威胁地球的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人必须一个不留全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲为了复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会将EXA-DB用于这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那样和维甘没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会使军事力量的平衡遭到破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让如今的联邦得到EXA-DB太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我们暗中销毁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会找罪受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对它的能耐 我有切身体会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不会搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴洛诺克 改变轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？我可没收到他们的联络…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算去发生战斗的宇域吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的我行我素不是第一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 把适配器递给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人叫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这儿有点事 你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要和我们一起参加战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会追上你们的 别这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放任老人家自己去 不知会干出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷根本不听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的想法不可能轻易被改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真诚的交流绝不会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急着放弃 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷他一定明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变轨完成 锁定目标坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴洛诺克 全速航行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找那只怪物算账
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到接近它会如此困难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甄选出值得生存下去的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让人活得更有尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸计划将为我们打开通往新世界的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以把它理解成创造新的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知自己的所作所为 会造成怎样的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意听好 地球种们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘在此 宣布开始全面侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人全心为人类的未来着想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否愿意陪我的疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誓将人类 带往伊甸！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正逐渐发挥出雷吉鲁斯的全部性能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种距离下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐身斗篷？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士竟然也有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那原本就是来自EXA-DB的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德在成长过程中拥有 也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这块不算广阔的宇域里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EXA-DB可以隐匿至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来和那种能力有密切关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在出去也只会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冯法尔西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少可以成为杰哈特大人的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解杰哈特大人的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能允许你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗宇域附近发现反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是机动战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错 是希德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去找出EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在火星上遇到过的维甘高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别来碍事 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我自己的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是在考验我作为伊泽尔坎特大人继承者的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝你别来插手 尽快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特的继承者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特 你这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和这东西有交战经验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少还记得它的行动规律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来吸引它 快逃 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全无影无踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船…船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 那颗小行星里藏着EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样永远无法捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如一试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锚索发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 看你往哪儿跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就在缆绳的末端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中攻击那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缆绳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掌握了！高达雷吉鲁斯的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于成功驾驭了高达雷吉鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了 被诅咒的秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是EXA-DB吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:20:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你摧毁它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我让开 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 EXA-DB不能留在世上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EXA-DB对我军来说是必不可少的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看见它造出怎样的怪物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 EXA-DB的力量是被诅咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有能力控制那样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是为了人类的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在确认EXA-DB是否完全被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是你说要打的 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EXA-DB…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去它或许令人惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我得到了高达雷吉鲁斯的全部能力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经继承了它
